    "description": "Last Mind Standing is a first person shooter that takes place inside a very powerful mind, trained to defend itself against intruders at all cost.<br><br>Lots of powers, wepons and abilities at your disposal to decimate everything in sight. Avoid all obstacles and traps. Keep moving, never stop.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071100/extras/fa3e5fcc2918c82334aa91f02f4b660a.poster.avif?t=1766851551\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071100/extras/fa3e5fcc2918c82334aa91f02f4b660a.webm?t=1766851551\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071100/extras/fa3e5fcc2918c82334aa91f02f4b660a.mp4?t=1766851551\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>-Left hand: Powers.<br>-Right hand: Weapons.<br>-Leg: Melee (and Parry!)<br>You can use all of them at once.<br><br>Ammo? Who needs that. Just mow down enemies and parry projectiles to fill up the meter and then use your powers to cause even more destruction, or heal yourself if you need it.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071100/extras/fa0f5fe934f085e9619f691cbfb6a60e.poster.avif?t=1766851551\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071100/extras/fa0f5fe934f085e9619f691cbfb6a60e.webm?t=1766851551\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071100/extras/fa0f5fe934f085e9619f691cbfb6a60e.mp4?t=1766851551\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Pay attention to your surroundings. You never know where your subconscious will place some helpful upgrades that will give you some peace of mind.<br><br>Abhorrent creations. Impossible places. Relentless enemies. Deathly traps. Legit nightmare fuel. Will you let them stop you?<br><br>Difficulty selection and three game modes: Normal, Extra Lives and Permadeath.<br><br>Metal soundtrack and skippable cutscenes for those who only care about gameplay.<br><br>Are you ready to be… mind-blown?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071100/extras/88b2634cc3dbfc6a3dbd680b09567dfc.avif?t=1766851551\" width=614 height=240 /></span>",
